Bar Chart
--------------

```{r dimple-bar}
hair_eye = as.data.frame(HairEyeColor)
p2 <- dPlot(Freq ~ Hair, groups = 'Eye', 
  data = subset(hair_eye, Sex == "Female"), 
  type = 'bar'
)
p2$defaultColors(c('brown', 'blue', '#594c26', 'green'))
p2
```

```{r results = 'asis', comment = NA, echo = F}
make_edit_button('dimple-bar')
```

