Area Chart
-------------------

```{r dimple-area}
dat <- data.frame(
  t = rep(0:23, each = 4), 
  var = rep(LETTERS[1:4], 4), 
  val = round(runif(4*24,0,50))
)
p8 <- dPlot(val ~ t, groups =  'var', data = dat, 
 type = 'area'
)
p8
```

```{r results = 'asis', comment = NA, echo = F}
make_edit_button('dimple-area')
```

